  "prompt": "Can we load money in multi wallet ICICI card?",
  "response": "Yes, you can load money onto your ICICI multi-wallet card. The process typically involves transferring funds from your bank account or through other means such as cash deposits at designated locations. To load money onto your ICICI multi-wallet card, you should:\n\n1. **Log in to your ICICI Internet Banking**: If you have an account, you can log in and navigate to the relevant section for wallet services.\n2. **Use the ICICI Mobile App**: If you have the ICICI Bank mobile app, you can also manage your wallet and load funds directly from your mobile device.\n3. **Bank Transfer**: Use NEFT/RTGS/UPI to transfer funds from your bank account to your wallet.\n4. **Visit an ATM or bank branch**: Some ATMs might have an option to load money directly onto your card, or you can deposit cash at a branch or through a partner store.\n\nEnsure you check for any applicable fees or limits on how much you can load into your multi-wallet and verify with ICICI Bank for the most accurate and updated procedures.",
